System Requirements
Operating Systems
The Kendo UI for Angular suite is OS agnostic.
Node.js
The required Node.js version is 10.9.0 or later. Alongside the Node.js installation, a supported NPM version will be installed. You can also install Kendo UI for Angular components with third-party package managers such as Yarn.
To check your Node.js version, run node -v in a terminal or console window.
Angular
Kendo UI for Angular supports the latest official Angular version and those currently under long-term support (LTS). For more details, refer to the Support Policy and Schedule article in the official Angular documentation.
To check your Angular version, run ng v in a terminal or console window.
Browsers
Kendo UI for Angular supports the major browsers as Angular does. For more details, refer to the Browser Support article in the official Angular documentation.
